flowchart TD
    A[Start Reconciliation Phase] --> B[Auditor compares:<br/>Initial DECOR, Ticket Map, implementation, tests, docs]
    B --> C[Auditor classifies drift<br/>governance / invariant / architectural / implementation / test / documentation / naming / namespace / identity]
    C --> D[Architect performs structural reconciliation<br/>updates DECOR surfaces + metadata]
    D --> E[Reconciled DECOR drafted<br/>reconciled-decor.md]
    E --> F[Auditor writes session-logs/03-reconciliation-log.md]

    F --> G{Epilogue required?}
    G -- No --> H[Verification Phase begins<br/>Verifier executes golden, dark, governance, replay tests]
    G -- Yes --> R1[Reconciliation Phase: Epilogue Handling (if required)]

    R1 --> R2[Orchestrator generates epilogue tickets<br/>after Auditor drift classification]
    R2 --> R3[Implementer (delegated from Implementation Mode)<br/>executes epilogue ticket: code, tests, session-logs/, replay-traces/]
    R3 --> R4[Auditor validates corrections<br/>drift resolved?]
    R4 --> R5{All drift resolved?}
    R5 -- No --> R2
    R5 -- Yes --> R6[Verifier (delegated from Verification Mode)<br/>validates corrective ticket outputs]
    R6 --> R7{Corrective outputs valid?}
    R7 -- No --> R2
    R7 -- Yes --> R8[Architect updates Reconciled DECOR if needed]
    R8 --> H

    H --> I{All verification checks pass?}
    I -- No --> D
    I -- Yes --> J[Closure Phase<br/>Orchestrator + Curator]

    J --> K[Epilogue actions finalised<br/>closure report + archival]
    K --> L[Tranche closed]
